OL,3,CLevy on gambling companies to raise
OL,4,C#100m to help tackle addiction
OL,6,FA levy on casino and betting
OL,7,Foperators' profits will bring in #100
OL,8,Fmillion to help tackle problem
OL,9,Fgambling, the government has announced.
OL,11,FUnder the plans, a statutory levy will
OL,12,Fbe imposed on gambling operators, with
OL,13,Fhalf of the money going directly to
OL,14,FNHS-led treatment and support, the
OL,15,FDepartment for Culture, Media and
OL,16,FSport (DCMS) confirmed.
OL,18,FOnline slot stakes will also be
OL,19,Flimited under the efforts to
OL,20,Fstrengthen legislation on gambling
OL,21,Faddiction.
