OL,3,CLevy on gambling companies to raise
OL,4,C#100m to help tackle addiction
OL,6,FThe mandatory levy aims to make
OL,7,Fconsistent contributions from gambling
OL,8,Foperators to a ringfenced fund to
OL,9,Fprevent and tackle gambling harm.
OL,11,FA voluntary system is currently in
OL,12,Fplace, which means some operators pay
OL,13,Fas little as #1 a year towards
OL,14,Fresearch, prevention and treatment.
OL,16,FThe new system will charge a levy to
OL,17,Fall licensed gambling operators at
OL,18,Fdifferent rates to take into account
OL,19,Fthe difference in operating costs and
OL,20,Flevels of harmful gambling.
