OL,3,CLevy on gambling companies to raise
OL,4,C#100m to help tackle addiction
OL,6,FThe government will also introduce
OL,7,Fstake limits for online slots of #5
OL,8,Fper spin for adults aged 25 and over
OL,9,Fand #2 per spin for 18 to 24-year-olds.
OL,11,FGambling minister Baroness Twycross
OL,12,Fsaid: "We are absolutely committed to
OL,13,Fimplementing strengthened measures for
OL,14,Fthose at risk, as well as providing
OL,15,Feffective support for those affected.
OL,17,F"The introduction of the first legally
OL,18,Fmandated levy will be instrumental in
OL,19,Fsupporting research, raising awareness
OL,20,Fand reducing the stigma around
OL,21,Fgambling-related harm."
