OL,3,CLevy on gambling companies to raise
OL,4,C#100m to help tackle addiction
OL,6,FOf the funding from the levy, 50% will
OL,7,Fgo to NHS England and bodies in
OL,8,FScotland and Wales for gambling
OL,9,Fsupport and treatment systems, from
OL,10,Freferrals and triage through to
OL,11,Frecovery and aftercare.
OL,13,FAnother 30% will be invested in
OL,14,Fmeasures such as national public
OL,15,Fhealth campaigns and training for
OL,16,Ffrontline staff, while the remaining
OL,17,F20% will be used for a research
OL,18,Fprogramme on gambling to be developed
OL,19,Fby UK Research and Innovation.
