OL,6,FSome 2.5% of the population gamble in
OL,7,Fa "severe and harmful way" and many
OL,8,Fmore people are affected, including
OL,9,Ffamily members and problem gamblers
OL,10,Fwho are below the clinical threshold,
OL,11,FProfessor Henrietta Bowden-Jones,
OL,12,Fnational clinical adviser on gambling
OL,13,Fharms at NHS England, said.
