OL,3,CLevy on gambling companies to raise
OL,4,C#100m to help tackle addiction
OL,6,FClaire Murdoch, NHS national director
OL,7,Ffor mental health, said the issue has
OL,8,F"skyrocketed" and welcomed the
OL,9,Fgovernment's commitment to a mandatory
OL,10,Fgambling levy.
OL,12,F"Problem gambling can completely ruin
OL,13,Flives and the issue has skyrocketed,
OL,14,Fwith NHS services treating record
OL,15,Fnumbers and our latest data showing a
OL,16,Fstaggering 129% increase in service
OL,17,Freferrals compared with the same
OL,18,Fperiod last year."
