OL,3,CLevy on gambling companies to raise
OL,4,C#100m to help tackle addiction
OL,6,FWill Prochaska, an independent
OL,7,Fcampaigner for gambling reform, said:
OL,8,F"We wouldn't allow Big Tobacco to
OL,9,Fcontrol lung cancer clinics and we
OL,10,Fmustn't allow Big Gambling to control
OL,11,Fmental health services.
OL,13,F"The purpose of the statutory levy is
OL,14,Fto remove gambling industry influence,
OL,15,Fand it can't come soon enough."
